845
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:02,620
Little one, tell me what you want.

846
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:04,220
Sour, sweet, bitter,

847
00:36:04,660 --> 00:36:05,260
or spicy?

848
00:36:05,560 --> 00:36:07,360
Sour means boy, and spicy means girl.

849
00:36:11,060 --> 00:36:12,380
I wish to be alone.

850
00:36:19,693 --> 00:36:21,020
Her parents probably don't know

851
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:22,700
Yangyang is pregnant yet.

852
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:25,420
But there's something
I need to tell you.

853
00:36:27,220 --> 00:36:30,300
Yangyang was pampered growing up.

854
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,580
I really can't imagine

855
00:36:33,580 --> 00:36:35,100
how you two are going to raise a child.

856
00:36:35,582 --> 00:36:37,580
There's no way the three of you
live on takeout.

857
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:41,300
So,

858
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:42,580
what's your plan?

859
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:45,860
I don't think

860
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,540
Yangyang wants to keep the baby.

861
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:56,500
She must still be shaken.

862
00:37:01,100 --> 00:37:02,020
If...

863
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,700
If she's scared,

864
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,740
I can try to understand her.

865
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:10,940
And?

866
00:37:12,380 --> 00:37:13,500
Try to understand her?

867
00:37:15,100 --> 00:37:17,660
That's your whole plan?

868
00:37:23,604 --> 00:37:25,980
Captain Wu, how are you going to
deal with this ostrich?

869
00:37:26,580 --> 00:37:28,100
Let him figure it out himself.

870
00:37:30,260 --> 00:37:30,940
Fine.

871
00:37:31,671 --> 00:37:33,871
I'll take him somewhere
and help him think it through.

872
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:45,540
I don't need that.

873
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:48,380
It'll help you relieve stress.
Everyone experiences pain differently.

874
00:37:48,380 --> 00:37:50,960
The scale goes from level one to ten.
It lasts eight minutes.

875
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,660
You can stop anytime.

876
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:54,180
Thank you.

877
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:56,020
Ready when you are.

878
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:58,100
Nurse,

879
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:59,700
can you show me how to use this?

880
00:37:59,700 --> 00:38:00,940
Please come over here.

881
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:20,860
Level five.

882
00:38:29,060 --> 00:38:29,780
Level nine.

883
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:39,140
Level ten. Ready.

884
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:45,020
Okay.

885
00:38:50,980 --> 00:38:52,740
Morning sickness, and labor pain.

886
00:38:53,180 --> 00:38:54,380
What you just went through

887
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,604
is only the tip of the iceberg.

888
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:57,220
Yangyang studied medicine.

889
00:38:57,660 --> 00:38:59,580
She knows exactly
how painful childbirth is.

890
00:39:00,300 --> 00:39:01,860
That's not what she's afraid of.

891
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:03,100
If you wish to understand her,

892
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:06,260
you need to find out
what she's actually afraid of.

893
00:39:07,580 --> 00:39:09,100
This baby belongs to both of you.

894
00:39:09,648 --> 00:39:11,826
You should let her know
what you're thinking.

895
00:39:12,580 --> 00:39:13,660
And more than that,

896
00:39:14,780 --> 00:39:16,060
show her your resolve.

897
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:46,220
The number you've dialed
is currently unavailable.

898
00:39:46,260 --> 00:39:47,860
Please try again later.

899
00:40:35,180 --> 00:40:37,380
Excuse me, can I help you
with something?

900
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:40,140
No thanks. I'm just browsing.

901
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,100
Why are you sulking?

902
00:41:17,980 --> 00:41:19,140
Yangyang isn't picking up.

903
00:41:19,780 --> 00:41:20,860
I don't know where she is.

904
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:23,580
Look at you. All down in the dumps.

905
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:24,940
Forget Yangyang,

906
00:41:25,182 --> 00:41:26,740
even I don't feel like talking to you.

907
00:41:29,660 --> 00:41:30,540
Captain Wu.

908
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:32,900
What should I do?

909
00:41:47,141 --> 00:41:50,621
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

910
00:41:51,311 --> 00:41:54,581
♪So deep, so boundless♪

911
00:41:54,921 --> 00:41:58,091
♪Just like your arms♪

912
00:41:58,581 --> 00:42:01,701
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

913
00:42:01,991 --> 00:42:05,631
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

914
00:42:05,631 --> 00:42:12,051
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

915
00:42:12,551 --> 00:42:16,951
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

916
00:42:17,411 --> 00:42:20,501
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

917
00:42:21,291 --> 00:42:26,091
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

918
00:42:28,361 --> 00:42:30,201
♪I truly understand♪

919
00:42:30,691 --> 00:42:34,881
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

920
00:42:35,131 --> 00:42:41,101
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

921
00:42:41,607 --> 00:42:44,297
♪Using up all my fortune♪

922
00:42:44,301 --> 00:42:48,701
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

923
00:42:48,791 --> 00:42:51,011
♪Thank you for awakening♪

924
00:42:51,021 --> 00:42:56,101
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

925
00:42:56,241 --> 00:42:59,431
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

926
00:42:59,761 --> 00:43:03,291
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

927
00:43:03,371 --> 00:43:08,341
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

928
00:43:08,341 --> 00:43:12,331
♪No one can tear us apart♪

929
00:43:12,521 --> 00:43:15,871
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

930
00:43:16,131 --> 00:43:21,471
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

931
00:43:22,361 --> 00:43:26,351
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

932
00:43:26,601 --> 00:43:30,001
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

933
00:43:30,121 --> 00:43:34,651
♪No need to call out loudly♪

934
00:43:34,651 --> 00:43:37,321
♪No matter how much it takes♪

935
00:43:37,341 --> 00:43:41,751
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

936
00:43:41,751 --> 00:43:45,011
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

937
00:43:45,031 --> 00:43:49,081
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

938
00:43:49,081 --> 00:43:52,551
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

939
00:43:52,551 --> 00:43:56,321
♪Only by your side♪

940
00:43:56,331 --> 00:44:03,411
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
